        {
            "title": "早市滬升深挫 金礦股受捧 紫金漲逾半成",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬深股市今早齊齊高開後掉頭向下，滬市半日尚能報升，深市則反覆倒跌。金價再創新高，金礦股明顯強勢，紫金礦業(02899)A股(601899.SH)漲逾半成。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20241016_CR_source-web_Gold_01.jpg.webp\">\n<img src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20241016_CR_source-web_Gold_01.jpg.webp\"/>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">上證綜指今早高開8點後，於早市大部份時間報升，中段最高曾報4160點，升24點，但亦不止一次倒跌，於上午約11時見半日低位4124點，跌11點，其後才重新轉升；滬指中午收報4141點，升4點或0.12%，半日成交1萬億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">深證成指相對跑輸，今早高開52點後於初段升幅曾擴大至93點，衝上14532點便暫時無以為繼，開市不足15分鐘便轉跌，低位14279點，挫160點，尾市跌幅略為收窄；深指中午收報14332點，跌106點或0.74%，成交1.24萬億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬深300指數升12點或0.27%，收報4715點；創業板指數則跌28點或0.86%，報3320點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"紫金礦業官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/10/02899-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"紫金礦業官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/10/02899-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">紫金礦業官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">以金礦股為首的有色金屬板塊受捧，是支撐滬市邁向四連升的主力之一。紫金A股中午收報39.92元，升6.28%，以181.42億元交投成為滬市A股成交額榜首；山東黃金(01787)A股(600547.SH)升6.25%，報53.87元；赤峰黃金(06693)A股(600988.SH)也升6.18%，報41.22元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">石油行業同樣造好，中國海油(00883)A股(600938.SH)漲6.53%，報33.45元；中國石油(00857)A股(601857.SH)升5.29%，報10.35元；中國石化(00386)A股(600028.SH)也升4.72%，報6.44元。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：藍思科技官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/12/20250401_FI_source-web_06613-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：藍思科技官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/12/20250401_FI_source-web_06613-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：藍思科技官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">相反，不少在深圳掛牌的重磅股受壓，則拖低深市。藍思科技(06613)A股(300433.SZ)便挫8.45%，報39元；三花智控(02050)A股(002050.SZ)跌3.59%，報52.1元；寧德時代(03750)A股(300750.SZ)也跌1.13%，報343.08元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15612103-%e6%97%a9%e5%b8%82%e6%bb%ac%e5%8d%87%e6%b7%b1%e6%8c%ab-%e9%87%91%e7%a4%a6%e8%82%a1%e5%8f%97%e6%8d%a7-%e7%b4%ab%e9%87%91%e6%bc%b2%e9%80%be%e5%8d%8a%e6%88%90",
